        [ a bf:Note ;
            rdfs:label "Includes a bonus sound disc and booklet \"The time of bells, 2: soundscapes of Finland, Norway, Italy and Greece\" featuring audio soundscapes of cathedral bells of Turku, Finland and Oslo, Norway, bells and brass bands of May Day in Oslo, festival bells and bagpipes of Basilicata, Southern Italy, and carnival bells of Skyros, Greece. The disc was produced and recorded by Steven Feld in 2004."@en ],
